des:
If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email: perryapp@perry.it 
Amazon Alexa and the Perry home products work together to help you control home appliance nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light. 
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your Perry products in a few simple steps:
1) Download our "Perry Timer" app in android or ios app market;
2) Register one Perry account in our "Perry Timer" app;
3) You need to have some Perry devices in hand;
4) Configure these devices in our Perry app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Perry Timer" skills;
5) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market;
6) Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
7) Search "Perry Timer" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
8) Click Enable skill of "Perry Timer", and you'll be navigated to Perry login page;
9) Input your Perry account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
10) Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
Currently this skill supports products:
smart switch, smart socket, …
